Class NslArcTan

java.lang.Object
  nslj.src.lang.NslBase

          nslj.src.math.NslArcTan

public final class NslArcTan
extends NslUnaryOperator

ArcTan routines. There are two basic format for the evaluation method in this routine: 1, eval(a) -> c a is the parameter of the evaluation function to do atan(a) pointwise and the result is passed out as c 2. eval(dest, a) -> c a, b are the parameter of the evaluation function and dest is the temporary space to hold the result. The method returns the reference to dest.
